  last ~30 minutes. We'll mostly be discussing your experience and what you'
 re looking for in your next job. I will also share more about Journal's bus
 iness\, team\, and culture. Attached\, please find a pdf that includes more
  details about the Senior Backend Engineer position.\n\nTalk soon\,\nSam
