UID:6ugdoifvqu7vf4ghrgeacna6mu@google.com
CREATED:20191210T193925Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Hi Aaron\,</p><p>Thank you so much for taking the time to co
 me onsite and meet with the team! I have you confirmed to come in this&nbsp
 \;<strong>Thursday\, December 12th.</strong>&nbsp\;Please find your full sc
 hedule below:<br><br><strong>Thursday\, 12/12 (PT)</strong><br>12:15pm - 12
 :30pm: Adam Gefkovicz<br>12:30pm - 1:30pm: Gil Feig + Clayton Schubiner<br>
 1:30pm - 2:00pm: Connor Hayes<br>2:00pm - 2:15pm: Break<br>2:15pm - 3:00pm:
  Austin Connelly<br>3:00pm - 4:00pm: Liam Kinney<br>4:00pm - 4:30pm: Ben He
 rman</p><p><strong>Location:<br></strong><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/TDK8x
 WXhRxrJyQ8z8">55 2nd Street</a><br><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/TDK8xWXhRxr
 JyQ8z8">3rd Floor\, Suite 325</a></p><p><strong>Transportation:<br></strong
 >Please enter the building at 55 2nd Street and check in at the security de
 sk and they will let you up to the 3rd floor. We will be in Suite 325.</p><
 p>If you are driving\, there is a parking garage on the back side of the bu
 ilding\, located at 22 Anthony Street\, between 1st and 2nd. The parking ga
 rage is valet staffed and open to the general public from 6:00am to 8:00pm 
 Monday through Friday. We do however recommend taking public transportation
  as our office building is walking distance from the Bart / Muni stations.<
 /p><p><strong>Preparation:</strong></p><ul><li>You will likely be asked to 
 present a form of identification to our building security before being let 
 up to the 19th floor - this is normal! Please feel free to contact me direc
 tly at (<strong>407-929-3033</strong>) if there are any issues checking in.
 </li><li>Dress comfortably - we’re a pretty laid back team.</li></ul><p>Ple
 ase confirm that this works on your end and don’t hesitate to reach out if 
 you need anything before Thursday. We’re all very excited to meet you!<br><
 br>Very Best\,&nbsp\;<br>Alexis</p>
