DESCRIPTION:<br>Hi Aaron\,<br><br>My name is Annie Jacobsen and I am the Di
 rector of People at Elevate.<br><br>We’re excited to have you come in to me
 et the team! You are confirmed for an onsite interview on&nbsp\;<b>January 
 14th\, from 10:30 to approximately 4:30.</b><br><br>You will be meeting wit
 h a few engineers on the team as well as:<ul><li>Jesse Pickard\, Founder &a
 mp\; CEO</li><li>Andrew Maguire\, COO</li></ul><ul><li>Antón Morant\, Direc
 tor of Product Engineering</li></ul><br><br>Our office is located at&nbsp\;
 <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/ZyPogeFEb3K2">1479 Folsom St\, San Francisco\,
  CA 94103</a>. To find our office\, enter the alley off Folsom and look for
  a blue sign with an “e”. When you arrive\, please knock on the door and we
 'll let you in. If you have any issues getting to the office\, please text/
 call me at 408-655-7107. Feel free to show up just a few minutes before the
  interview start time.<br><br>Olivia Johnson\, our Employee Success Manager
