UID:1l5l9uobfho9egq2lvd4bfctbg@google.com
CREATED:20191217T230219Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Hi Aaron\,</p><p><br>I hope you're having a great week! My n
 ame is Olivia Bae\, and I am a recruiting coordinator working closely with 
 Sukie at Stripe!</p><p><br></p><p>Thanks for your patience as I've worked t
 o put together your&nbsp\;onsite&nbsp\;schedule. The team&nbsp\;is excited 
 to have&nbsp\;you&nbsp\;come to our office\, and&nbsp\;I've arranged your i
 nterviews to take place on&nbsp\;<b>Thursday\, December 19th</b>. I&nbsp\;h
 ave your start time listed as<b>&nbsp\;02:30pm PST</b>\, and&nbsp\;I’d sugg
 est aiming to arrive about 10 minutes before your first interview.&nbsp\;I’
 ve outlined your tentative schedule\, but please let me know if&nbsp\;you&n
 bsp\;have any questions at all.</p><p><br></p><p>I've also included links t
 o detailed directions for getting to our office [0]\, more information abou
 t what to expect on the day of your interview [1]\, and a quick guide to St
 ripe’s culture [2].&nbsp\;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><b>Office Location</
 b></p><p>We’re located at&nbsp\;<u><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/pla
 ce/510+Townsend+St\,+San+Francisco\,+CA+94103/@37.773728\,-122.402568\,17z/
 data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x808f7fd4a3999ec1:0x6510b30fb3274534!8m2!3d37.7737
 28!4d-122.4003793">510 Townsend St.\, San Francisco</a></u>&nbsp\;(near the
  intersection of Townsend and 6th Street). The main entrance is located und
 erneath the building number and 'Stripe' sign. Proceed to the reception des
 k to check in\; when checking in at reception\, let them know that you're h
 ere for an interview and that you are meeting with Cassie Alter\, my collea
 gue. Cassie will come greet you on my behalf as I will be out of the office
 .</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><b>Onsite Interview Schedule -</b>&nbsp\;<b>T
 hursday\, December 19th</b></p><p><br></p><p>02:15pm-02:30pm PST: Cassie Al
 ter\, my colleague\, will greet you<br>02:30pm-03:15pm PST: Experience and 
 Goals - Kenny Wolf<br>03:15pm-04:00pm PST: Technical Roleplay - Mikito Taka
 da and Evan Broder<br>04:00pm-04:15pm PST: Evan will walk you out!<br></p><
 p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Stripe will cover your transportation costs to and 
 from the office on the day of your interviews\;&nbsp\;because of the limite
 d parking available near the office\, we recommend using public transportat
 ion\, taxis\, or rideshare services. If you are interested in receiving rei
 mbursement for your transportation\, you'll have up to&nbsp\;2 business day
 s&nbsp\;after your interview date to submit your receipts using our reimbur
 sement tool\, Expensify [3].&nbsp\;Reimbursement is typically completed in 
 1 week.&nbsp\;</p><p><br></p><p>Please let me know if there is anything els
 e I can do! Looking forward to your visit! :)</p><p><br></p><p>All the best
 \,</p><p>Olivia</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>[0]&nbsp\;<u><a href="https://d
 ocs.google.com/document/d/1J5h2GKDs7SLILtCOf6DRC7CQW7dLnvkqWLt7SDEk-uA/edit
 #">Directions to Stripe SF</a></u></p><p>[1]&nbsp\;<u><a href="https://docs
 .google.com/document/d/1WGUWEsI1PELzry4f0MgD11dO67CmrXVBWumGnFff6-M/edit?us
