CREATED:20191218T160253Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Hi Aaron\,</p><p>We've scheduled&nbsp\;an in-house interview
  for&nbsp\;Wednesday December 18\, 3:00pm PST. The interview will be at our
  offices at:&nbsp\;548 4th Street in San Francisco\, CA.<br><br>You'll find
  a frosted door there\; please ring the blue doorbell\, to the left\, wait 
 for the buzzer and come on in. Before the glass doors to enter the actual o
 ffice space\, you'll see another doorbell. Just ring that and someone will 
 come to let you in.&nbsp\;<br><br>You can proceed to sign in on the iPad. Y
 ou can say you're here to see your first interviewer (listed below) and you
 'll be printed a name badge. Feel free to wait&nbsp\;in the reception area\
 , as a member of our team will greet you shortly after.<br><br>Here's some 
 more information for your day:&nbsp\;<a href="http://www.dominodatalab.com/
 careers/welcome">Domino Interview FAQ</a>&nbsp\; Username: domino Password:
  goodluck<br><br>Below is the interview schedule for your time here at Domi
 no. We also may have a few conversations outside the scheduled ones:<br><br
 >3:00pm-4:00pm PST: Chris Yang\, CTO<br>4:00pm-5:00pm PST: Madhavan Thiruma
 lai\, VP of Engineering<br><br>If you are interviewing for an engineering o
 r design role please bring your own laptop so you can be more comfortable i
 n your own development environment. If not possible\, we will provide one f
 or you.&nbsp\;<br><br>Let us know if&nbsp\;this time no longer works or if 
 you have any questions about your time here.<br><br>Otherwise\, we're excit
 ed&nbsp\;to meet you!<br><br>Thanks\,<br>Domino Team&nbsp\;</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20191218T162654Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Interview with Domino Data Lab
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
