DESCRIPTION:<strong>Preparation</strong><ul><li>Please bring your own lapto
 p with your dev environment set up.</li><li>Dress comfortably - we’re a pre
 tty laid back team.</li><li>Bring good questions to ask your non-technical 
 interviewers\, it’s a great chance to show that you’re thoughtful and want 
 to learn more about the company.</li></ul><strong>What to expect</strong><u
 l><li>You’ll drive a pair programming session with an engineer to test your
  algorithmic complexity in the context of something you might encounter wor
 king at Coinbase.</li><li>You’ll navigate a pair programming session with a
 n engineer to work on a domain related problem.</li><li>You’ll meet with en
 gineering leaders\, and will have a chance to ask them questions about Coin
 base\, its strategy and goals.</li>...</ul>
LAST-MODIFIED:20191220T213116Z
LOCATION:430 California Street\, San Francisco\, CA 94104
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Coinbase | ONSITE Interview
TRANSP:OPAQUE
