 o of the VIN (located in driver's door-jamb or at the base of the windshiel
 d)\n3. Photo of the front of your vehicle\n\nOnce received\, we will send y
 ou the Vehicle Purchase Agreement and additional paperwork to complete elec
 tronically.\n\n\nThanks!\n\nLocation: This is a Zoom web conference.\n\nYou
  can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps:
 //carvana.zoom.us/j/91472005634\n\nOne tap mobile:\n+1 312 626 6799\,\,9147
 2005634#\n+1 646 876 9923\,\,91472005634#\n\nYou can also dial in using you
 r phone.\nUS: +1 312 626 6799\, +1 646 876 9923\, +1 301 715 8592\, +1 346 
 248 7799\, +1 669 900 6833\, +1 253 215 8782\nMeeting ID: 914-720-05634\n\n
 Find your local number: https://carvana.zoom.us/u/acitAai73f\n\nPlease shar
 e where you would like your vehicle picked-up from. (Your eligibility is ba
 sed on the pickup address inputted on the website. You must be within Carva
 na's market to continue):\nMy home\n281 castle glen rd\nWalnut creek\, ca 9
 4595\n\nVIN: 1C4RJFAG1FC653138\n\nDid you update your payment method to ACH
