 e.  We also have a few designated parking spaces near our rear entrance\, b
 ut if all of those spaces are full\, there is also a parking garage on Rail
 road Avenue. We apologize in advance for any inconvenience!\n\nWinner of Di
 ablo&#39\;s Best of the East Bay Award\, Uncle Yu&#39\;s delivers Asian cui
 sine with a twist.\n\nInnovative Asian cuisine enhanced with quality ingred
 ients\, paired with a Wine Spectator Award winning wine list\, striking atm
 osphere and engaging service create the perfect dining experience.\n\nWheth
 er you desire a quick bite\, a fantastic glass of wine\, a meal with the fa
 mily or a sommelier&#39\;s wine paired dinner\, Uncle Yu&#39\;s delivers! \
 n\nIn addition to our dining room\, we have a lively lounge and bar\, a bea
 utiful outdoor patio and a private room for special occasions and holiday p
 arties.\n
