 ve to be mutually exclusive with social distancing and all of these Zoom ha
 ppy hours lack direction.\n\n1 game with 4 rounds\, 8 questions each. The q
 uestions will be in the presentation and the answers will be submitted via 
 the answer sheet provided below.\n\nAnswer Sheet (https://forms.gle/zVkA2Qe
 VuHMFDfNo9)  (This sheet gets re-used for every round)\n\nRound 4 will be a
  music round!\n\nTeams are encouraged! Just make sure you set up a separate
  chat of some sort to deliberate and that only one person is submitting ans
 wers for you guys. ("not green" text messaging\, whatsapp\, hangouts or som
 ething along those lines works best)\n\nIf you have suggestions for questio
 ns (either a specific question or a theme/topic)\, send them my way!
