 Hey Brian!\n      So sorry for the delayed response from Isaac's intro i ha
 ve been out of town.\n      I am heading up a project over here at Playstud
 ios in Burlingame which is really exciting! The project is going to require
  a substantially high volume of battery operated BLE transmitters pre-progr
 ammed to utilize the PXP exchange to interact with the apple iBeacon api as
  well as the associated Android proximity apis.\n\n      Playstudios has pa
 rtnered with the MGM Corporation which owns and operates the majority of th
 e high profile casinos on the Las Vegas Strip. We are looking to blanket al
 l of these casinos with beacons and offer some amazing features on top of t
 his infrastructure. On top of this we have 2 other high profile partners in
 terested in similar implementations at their locations.\n      I would real
 ly like to meet up and talk logistics to see if we can work together.\n\n\n
 \n      Aaron Jones\n\n\n\n      On Thu\, Dec 19\, 2013 at 3:18 PM\, Isaac 
