DESCRIPTION:Join us for a day party ("Darty") to celebrate Bay to Breakers!
 \n\nThe race starts at 8am. Feel free to come by anytime after 10am - morni
 ng or afternoon. \n\nWe'll have bagels for breakfast/brunch\, order some fo
 od for lunch and a keg of beer! \n\nGiven our placement along the run route
  it may be slightly challenging to navigate across the city to our place. T
 ake a peak at Google Maps before you head out. If you live in the city and 
 prefer to bike here\, you can stash your bike in the garage. There is also 
 a Lyft bike station around the corner (Grove & Masonic)
LAST-MODIFIED:20260404T063844Z
LOCATION:143 Ashbury St\, San Francisco\, CA 94117\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bay2Breakers
TRANSP:OPAQUE
