DESCRIPTION:<span><b>Caitlin and I moved into our new home in October. We’d
  love for you all to join us for a housewarming + holiday kickoff on Saturd
 ay\, December 4th.&nbsp\;</b></span><b><br><p>We’ll have drinks (beer\, kom
 bucha\, cocktail ingredients\, etc) and apps set out by 3pm\, so feel free 
 to come by anytime thereafter. We can order pizzas or other food for dinner
  depending on how the night is going. Feel free to bring a 6 pack or other 
 drink/alcohol if there’s something in particular you want to drink.&nbsp\;<
 /p><p>Festive / holiday attire optional\, but potentially encouraged?&nbsp\
 ;</p><p>If you plan to drive\, there is plenty of street parking in the nei
 ghborhood\, just don’t leave anything visible in your car.&nbsp\;</p><p>Can
 ’t wait to see you!</p></b>
