 dually\, if you can't make it.\n\nBrian\n\n1.  Please join my meeting.\nhtt
 ps://global.gotomeeting.com/join/333601765 \n \n2.  Use your microphone and
  speakers (VoIP) - a headset is recommended.  Or\, call in using your telep
 hone.\n \nUnited States: +1 (312) 757-3119\nUnited States (toll-free): 1 87
 7 309 2070\n \nAccess Code: 333-601-765\nAudio PIN: Shown after joining the
  meeting\n \nMeeting ID: 333-601-765
