DESCRIPTION:<html-blob>Hey everyone! <br><br>Join us for a day party ("Dart
 y") to celebrate the comeback of Bay to Breakers. <br><br>The race starts a
 t 8am. Feel free to come by anytime after 9:30am - morning or afternoon. We
 'll be making breakfast/brunch and serving drinks throughout the day so fee
 l free to show up whenever works best for you! <br><br>Given our placement 
 along the run route it may be slightly challenging to navigate across the c
 ity to our place. Take a peak at Google Maps before you head out. If you li
 ve in the city and prefer to bike here\, we can store your bike in the gara
 ge. <br><br>We're planning this pretty far ahead\, but wanted to get the wo
 rd out early. Tentative Yes' &amp\; Maybe's will help us plan for how much 
 food &amp\; drink to buy. Let us know if you're coming for breakfast and ha
 ve any dietary restrictions that we don't already know about.&nbsp\;Feel fr
 ee to BYO if there's something in particular you want to drink. And if ther
 e's anyone we missed or that you want to bring along\, the more the merrier
 !&nbsp\;<br><br>Does anyone own a cornhole set and want to bring it?!<br><b
 r>Let's do this!<br><br>Caitlin &amp\; Alex </html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260404T063843Z
LOCATION:143 Ashbury St\, San Francisco\, CA 94117\, USA
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Bay2Breakers Darty 
